verbose_text: It was observed that the mRNA expression of RORC in PDN group (0.72 +/- 0.17) was significantly lower than that in control group (1.53 +/- 0.17) (p < 0.01, Figure XREF_FIG a) and the mRNA expression of RORC in PDN + CTK group (0.86 +/- 0.21) was significantly lower than that in CTK group (1.83 +/- 0.22) (p < 0.01, Figure XREF_FIG a).
